# Three.js + React three fiber workshop for kids aged 10-12

## General rules

1. Create robust and idiomatic Three.js components using React Three Fiber.
2. Ensure the code follows best practices and is easy to understand.
3. All annotations and UI must be in Russian language.
4. Do no more no less than what I asked.
5. Follow the instructions carefully and ask questions if you need help.
6. We are going to develop in small increments iteratively.

## Workshop

The goal of the workshop is to teach some basics of programming with Three.js and React Three Fiber.

### Plot

In the workshop we are going to develop a simple 3D scene with a pool, and balls falling into it.
